WEBVTT

00:01.734 --> 00:08.006
♪

00:08.008 --> 00:09.174
[ticking]

00:12.745 --> 00:15.614
[ticking]

00:15.616 --> 00:16.681
[sigh]

00:21.187 --> 00:22.120
[gasp]

00:22.122 --> 00:23.622
Was that the Pony Post?

00:25.024 --> 00:27.626
Oh, it was just you, Opal.

00:30.863 --> 00:33.231
Every other day he's
here like clockwork.

00:33.233 --> 00:36.268
But not today! What could
possibly be holding him up?

00:37.236 --> 00:39.804
Strawberry Cinnamon
Cilantro Salutations!

00:39.806 --> 00:40.872
What?

00:40.874 --> 00:43.942
I bet you're wondering what
warrants such a welcome.

00:43.944 --> 00:46.678
Well, that welcome is warranted
by a pony that whisked up

00:46.680 --> 00:49.581
a warm batch of Strawberry
Cinnamon Cilantro cupcakes!

00:50.950 --> 00:53.084
That strangely sickening
flavor combination

00:53.086 --> 00:54.953
sounds just as bad as it tastes.

00:54.955 --> 00:55.887
[gulp]

00:55.889 --> 00:56.988
Ugh.

00:56.990 --> 00:58.790
So I came here to
offer you some!

00:58.792 --> 01:01.927
After that visually descriptive
and disturbing endorsement,

01:01.929 --> 01:05.830
Oh! I almost forgot! I have
this letter for you, Rarity!

01:05.832 --> 01:07.666
The Post Pony was
going to deliver it,

01:07.668 --> 01:09.801
but after his Strawberry
Cinnamon Cilantro cupcake,

01:09.803 --> 01:11.903
he was feeling kind of queasy.

01:11.905 --> 01:13.338
And since I was
heading over anyway,

01:13.340 --> 01:15.874
I figured I could do it
for him. There you go!

01:15.876 --> 01:16.875
Oh!

01:16.877 --> 01:22.814
[muttering]

01:22.816 --> 01:23.982
[excited shriek]

01:23.984 --> 01:25.350
What's it say?

01:25.352 --> 01:26.718
I GOT IT!

01:26.720 --> 01:28.153
WOO HOO!

01:28.155 --> 01:29.621
Got what?

01:29.623 --> 01:31.623
I have been holding out
for the perfect location

01:31.625 --> 01:33.625
and it finally became available.

01:33.627 --> 01:38.930
So now I can fulfill my dream of
OPENING A BOUTIQUE IN CANTERLOT!

01:38.932 --> 01:42.167
I'M SO EXCITED, I THINK I'M
GOING TO LOSE MY CUPCAKES!

01:44.036 --> 01:47.772
♪

01:50.376 --> 01:54.012
<i>♪ My little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

01:54.014 --> 01:55.947
<i>♪ Aaaahhh </i>

01:55.949 --> 01:57.882
<i>♪ My little Pony </i>

01:57.884 --> 02:00.385
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be. ♪</i>

02:00.387 --> 02:02.153
<i>♪ My Little Pony </i>

02:02.155 --> 02:04.823
<i>♪ Until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me. ♪</i>

02:04.825 --> 02:06.825
<i>♪ Big adventure! </i>
<i>♪ Tons of fun </i>

02:06.827 --> 02:08.994
<i>♪ A beautiful heart!  ♪</i>
<i>Faithful and strong! ♪</i>

02:08.996 --> 02:11.162
<i>♪ Sharing kindness </i>
<i>♪ it's an easy feat </i>

02:11.164 --> 02:13.231
<i>♪ And magic makes it</i>
<i>all complete! ♪</i>

02:13.233 --> 02:15.266
<i>♪ To have my little pony </i>

02:15.268 --> 02:18.937
<i>♪ Do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

02:18.939 --> 02:21.373
♪

02:25.845 --> 02:29.147
[train chugging]

02:29.149 --> 02:30.849
♪

02:30.851 --> 02:33.018
Rarity's such a
savvy business pony!

02:33.020 --> 02:35.353
I'm so impressed she used
the huge bonus she earned

02:35.355 --> 02:38.356
making the costumes for Sapphire
Shores' Equestria-wide tour

02:38.358 --> 02:40.225
to open this
second boutique!

02:45.698 --> 02:47.832
[admiring chatter]

02:47.834 --> 02:51.002
I take it from your reaction
that you like the boutique.

02:51.004 --> 02:52.704
It's lovely.

02:52.706 --> 02:55.874
Gosh, Rarity, I know
hard work when I see it,

02:55.876 --> 02:58.209
and it looks like you worked
your hooves to the nub.

02:58.211 --> 03:02.113
I don't know. Those hooves don't
look nubby. They look scrubbied.

03:02.115 --> 03:03.982
And buffied. And pedied!

03:03.984 --> 03:08.119
Well, despite my nubby,
scrubby, buffy pony pedi,

03:08.121 --> 03:11.022
I actually have been
working very hard.

03:11.024 --> 03:13.024
However, I never could have
gotten the boutique ready

03:13.026 --> 03:17.696
without the help of my new
manager: Sassy Saddles!

03:22.802 --> 03:27.772
Bust my buttons, Rarity!
The Ponies from Ponyville!

03:27.774 --> 03:29.374
[greetings]

03:29.376 --> 03:32.343
I knew I needed a manager
for Canterlot Carousel.

03:32.345 --> 03:35.013
So when Sassy showed
me her resume and I saw

03:35.015 --> 03:38.083
that she'd worked in all the
finest boutiques in Canterlot,

03:38.085 --> 03:40.218
I hired her right
on the spot!

03:40.220 --> 03:43.221
I then laid out this
plan or "pattern"

03:43.223 --> 03:46.725
as we say in the fashion
biz, for Canterlot Carousel,

03:46.727 --> 03:50.095
so that Rarity's boutique
will be a guaranteed success

03:50.097 --> 03:54.099
and those doors will
never, ever, ever close!

03:54.101 --> 03:57.936
Wow, Sassy, your attention to
detail is truly impressive.

03:57.938 --> 04:01.439
I've already put a pin in the
first piece of the pattern,

04:01.441 --> 04:04.042
"Beautify the Boutique."

04:04.044 --> 04:07.278
But next was the very
crucial pattern piece,

04:07.280 --> 04:09.914
"Marketing to the Mares."

04:09.916 --> 04:14.486
Turns out that everypony
here loves royalty!

04:14.488 --> 04:17.789
So I created a collection that
beautifully revolves around

04:17.791 --> 04:19.758
the royal element of Canterlot.

04:19.760 --> 04:24.129
And it just so happens there's a
hot new princess in Equestria.

04:24.131 --> 04:26.064
In every poll
Sassy Saddles took,

04:26.066 --> 04:28.166
you were the most
popular Princess!

04:28.168 --> 04:31.236
Coincidentally, one of my gowns
is inspired by the window

04:31.238 --> 04:34.239
in Canterlot Castle
commemorating your coronation!

04:37.877 --> 04:39.978
[admiring chatter]

04:39.980 --> 04:43.148
While I've always prided myself
on paying attention to detail.

04:43.150 --> 04:45.917
I've taken my latest collection
to a whole new level

04:45.919 --> 04:48.186
with Rarity's Rules of TLC.

04:48.188 --> 04:51.990
Judging by this baby, TLC stands
for Tasty Licorice Candy!

04:53.325 --> 04:56.561
TLC stands for Time,
Love, and Couture.

04:56.563 --> 04:58.963
And while I do agree that
this dress has potential,

04:58.965 --> 05:01.299
I have not had enough Time
to give it enough Love

05:01.301 --> 05:02.534
to become Couture.

05:04.003 --> 05:06.004
But the rest of the
gowns in tonight's line

05:06.006 --> 05:09.040
have met Rarity's Rules and
are ready to be presented!

05:09.042 --> 05:12.243
My marketing research also
confirmed that customers

05:12.245 --> 05:14.445
that viewed somepony
famous wearing a gown

05:14.447 --> 05:17.448
wished to own that
gown for themselves.

05:17.450 --> 05:22.053
I call this piece of the
pattern "Celebrity Status."

05:22.055 --> 05:24.389
So, Twilight, we were
wondering if perhaps

05:24.391 --> 05:26.491
you might possibly
wear this tonight?

05:28.460 --> 05:30.395
If being a Princess
and wearing that dress

05:30.397 --> 05:33.364
can help your boutique
in any way, then I say...

05:33.366 --> 05:35.934
Stick a pin in it! It's done!

05:35.936 --> 05:39.337
All right, everypony!
Let's set the stage!

05:39.339 --> 05:41.206
Ever since I was a little filly,

05:41.208 --> 05:44.375
all I've ever wanted was to own
a boutique here in Canterlot.

05:44.377 --> 05:47.378
Somepony pinch me, I'm
about to open the doors

05:47.380 --> 05:49.347
to that very boutique!

05:49.349 --> 05:52.483
♪

05:52.485 --> 05:57.622
Welcome to the Grand Opening
of Canterlot Carousel!

05:57.624 --> 06:01.092
[cheers]

06:03.596 --> 06:05.964
Oh, hello! Nice to see you!

06:05.966 --> 06:09.334
Welcome, welcome! Oh, I'm
so happy you could make it!

06:09.336 --> 06:11.970
That Sassy totally stepped
on your hooves, Rarity!

06:11.972 --> 06:15.139
Oh, no! Did she mess
up that nice pony pedi?

06:15.141 --> 06:17.909
OK. Phew!

06:17.911 --> 06:20.278
Oh, I don't think she meant to.

06:20.280 --> 06:23.248
Rarity. Are you ready to
reveal the collection?

06:23.250 --> 06:26.251
Is she sure she doesn't
want to do it herself?

06:26.253 --> 06:28.186
[snorts] Yeah.

06:28.188 --> 06:31.923
Yes, I am. Fluttershy. Could
you help Twilight get ready?

06:31.925 --> 06:33.258
Oh, certainly.

06:35.327 --> 06:37.362
Fillies and Gentlecolts!

06:37.364 --> 06:40.431
I am designer and
couturier, Rarity!

06:40.433 --> 06:42.934
I would like to
welcome you again

06:42.936 --> 06:45.403
to the Grand Opening
of Canterlot Carousel!

06:45.405 --> 06:47.405
And I am thrilled that
you're here to see

06:47.407 --> 06:50.541
my newest collection
inspired by this regal city.

06:52.011 --> 06:56.381
[Oohs and ahs]

06:56.383 --> 06:58.683
<i>♪ [dance] </i>

06:58.685 --> 07:02.654
[exclamations continue]

07:02.656 --> 07:06.024
♪

07:06.026 --> 07:07.191
Rarity, I'm...

07:07.193 --> 07:10.128
Fashion Plate of
Cosmare Magazine!

07:10.130 --> 07:12.497
I'm so honored that Cosmare
was able to do a piece

07:12.499 --> 07:14.465
on the Grand Opening
of my boutique!

07:14.467 --> 07:17.068
Well, when Sassy Saddles
calls saying she's found

07:17.070 --> 07:18.670
the latest and
greatest in fashion,

07:18.672 --> 07:20.438
we high tail without fail!

07:20.440 --> 07:22.440
Now tell me all about
your latest collection.

07:22.442 --> 07:26.344
Ooh, uh. It's called
Rarity's Royal Regalia!

07:26.346 --> 07:28.012
[gasp] Royally radiant!

07:28.014 --> 07:30.448
My favorite part
of being a designer

07:30.450 --> 07:32.150
is finding my inspiration.

07:32.152 --> 07:34.686
And that really wasn't difficult
when it came to Canterlot.

07:34.688 --> 07:38.022
Everywhere I looked, the
royal city just spoke to me!

07:38.024 --> 07:40.558
I call it, "In-Spire-ation!"

07:40.560 --> 07:42.327
Genius! Simply genius!

07:42.329 --> 07:46.030
♪

07:46.032 --> 07:48.499
I spent hours by the lily
pond on the castle grounds,

07:48.501 --> 07:51.502
which inspired this
gown, "Water Filly."

07:51.504 --> 07:53.671
Oh, the whimsy!

07:53.673 --> 07:56.174
Watching Celestia raise
the sun each morning

07:56.176 --> 07:57.742
literally lit up my day!

07:59.178 --> 08:01.980
This is "Tripping the Light!"

08:01.982 --> 08:03.314
Fantastic!

08:03.316 --> 08:06.217
♪

08:06.219 --> 08:10.321
And of course, Luna raising
the moon guided me to sleep.

08:10.323 --> 08:12.657
I call this, "Over the Moon."

08:12.659 --> 08:14.192
Oooh!

08:14.194 --> 08:16.294
Well, I certainly am!

08:16.296 --> 08:19.664
And for our finale, I have
something very special.

08:19.666 --> 08:22.467
I was inspired by the
stained glass window

08:22.469 --> 08:24.769
created in honor of
Princess Twilight.

08:24.771 --> 08:28.473
So I call this, "The
Reign in Stain!"

08:28.475 --> 08:30.641
Because the dress is
inspired by the...

08:30.643 --> 08:33.411
stained glass window
of a reigning Princess!

08:33.413 --> 08:35.079
Yes!

08:35.081 --> 08:38.082
Well, I think "The
Reign in Stain"

08:38.084 --> 08:40.151
is too difficult
to explain!

08:40.153 --> 08:43.554
Especially for the signature
piece of a collection!

08:43.556 --> 08:44.489
But I rather like...

08:44.491 --> 08:46.657
Fillies and Gentlecolts!

08:46.659 --> 08:49.660
I, Sassy Saddles, am
pleased to introduce

08:49.662 --> 08:52.363
the Grand Finale of
the Grand Opening

08:52.365 --> 08:56.734
of Rarity's Royal Regalia!
"The Princess Dress!"

08:56.736 --> 09:01.339
♪

09:01.341 --> 09:02.673
[gasp] Success!

09:02.675 --> 09:05.176
[squeals]

09:05.178 --> 09:12.250
[excited chatter]

09:13.452 --> 09:15.553
Everypony! Please follow me

09:15.555 --> 09:20.224
and you can all place your
orders for...The Princess Dress!

09:20.226 --> 09:22.460
[chattering]

09:22.462 --> 09:25.363
Rarity, I want to be the first
pony to congratulate you.

09:25.365 --> 09:27.131
The Princess Dress
has just guaranteed

09:27.133 --> 09:28.733
Canterlot Carousel's success!

09:30.269 --> 09:33.304
[excited chatter]

09:33.306 --> 09:35.306
[squeals]

09:35.308 --> 09:38.443
Yeah! Rarity's Royal
Regalia is amazing.

09:38.445 --> 09:41.479
And everypony seemed to
love the Princess Dress!

09:41.481 --> 09:43.781
You bet your saddle they did!

09:43.783 --> 09:48.653
Rarity now has one hundred
orders for her signature gown!

09:48.655 --> 09:53.658
[stammering] One hundred
orders? All at one time?

09:53.660 --> 09:56.427
According to my pattern,
the next piece is

09:56.429 --> 09:58.663
"The Success of The
Signature Dress!"

09:58.665 --> 10:01.165
So, I do not see the problem!

10:02.701 --> 10:04.502
Uh...

10:04.504 --> 10:06.537
Cupcake!

10:06.539 --> 10:08.806
[ahem]

10:08.808 --> 10:12.110
First of all, Sassy Saddles,
I would have appreciated

10:12.112 --> 10:16.814
getting to name the final gown
from my collection myself.

10:16.816 --> 10:21.586
My research shows that
your "Reign in Stain" name

10:21.588 --> 10:24.322
was a play on words that
was both very confusing

10:24.324 --> 10:26.691
and quite unappealing.

10:26.693 --> 10:30.161
While I see your point, we
should have discussed it

10:30.163 --> 10:32.597
prior to the Grand
Opening, Sassy.

10:32.599 --> 10:36.467
My only goal is for Canterlot
Carousel to succeed!

10:36.469 --> 10:38.736
That's why I changed the name.

10:38.738 --> 10:43.641
And that is why I took all those
orders for the Princess Dress.

10:43.643 --> 10:47.445
But receiving orders for one
hundred dresses in one day

10:47.447 --> 10:50.381
is just too much too soon.

10:50.383 --> 10:54.785
Are you actually saying we
should cancel these orders?

10:54.787 --> 11:01.659
No, Sassy. Promises were made
and I shall sew my very best

11:01.661 --> 11:05.730
to provide each and every pony
a Princess Dress full of TLC!

11:05.732 --> 11:08.499
Oh, thank you,
Rarity! Thank you!

11:10.202 --> 11:11.402
[sigh]

11:16.875 --> 11:19.177
Satin and silk, Rarity!

11:19.179 --> 11:21.646
Are you sure you don't want
your friends to help you

11:21.648 --> 11:23.281
make the dresses?

11:23.283 --> 11:26.617
No, Sassy. These orders
are my responsibility.

11:26.619 --> 11:28.786
All I have to do
is stick to my plan

11:28.788 --> 11:31.289
so I can deliver each
and every Princess Dress

11:31.291 --> 11:34.225
in keeping with my
Rules of Rarity.

11:34.227 --> 11:41.299
♪

11:42.534 --> 11:44.969
<i>♪ The Rules of Rarity</i>
<i>Guaranteed Quality! ♪</i>

11:44.971 --> 11:47.271
<i>♪ This I can assure! </i>

11:47.273 --> 11:52.343
<i>♪ For each and every dress</i>
<i>I vow to give finesse ♪</i>

11:52.345 --> 11:55.446
♪ With Time, Love, and Couture

11:55.448 --> 12:02.520
♪

12:06.391 --> 12:10.995
<i>♪ My favorite moment's</i>
<i>when a pony sees it. ♪</i>

12:10.997 --> 12:15.900
<i>♪ That special gown</i>
<i>that she just adores ♪</i>

12:15.902 --> 12:20.838
<i>♪ That pony's now in style!</i>
<i>My hard work's all worthwhile ♪</i>

12:20.840 --> 12:26.277
<i>♪ Oh, yes, it makes my</i>
<i>heart, my heart, just soar! ♪</i>

12:26.279 --> 12:30.881
♪

12:30.883 --> 12:34.552
<i>♪ music slows </i>

12:34.554 --> 12:41.626
<i>♪</i>

12:51.870 --> 12:54.805
<i>♪ The Rules of Rarity</i>
<i>Just a parody ♪</i>

12:54.807 --> 12:57.608
<i>♪ No dress here's unique</i>

12:57.610 --> 13:03.281
<i>♪ The panels all the same</i>
<i>Each colored window pane ♪</i>

13:03.283 --> 13:08.386
<i>♪ My fashion only makes</i>
<i>me want to shriek! ♪</i>

13:08.388 --> 13:11.689
<i>♪ Oh, to create! </i>

13:11.691 --> 13:14.925
<i>♪ Would give me elation! </i>

13:14.927 --> 13:19.363
<i>♪ To feel once again</i>
<i>some inspiration! ♪</i>

13:19.365 --> 13:20.965
<i>♪</i>

13:20.967 --> 13:25.803
<i>♪ Come on now, Rarity!</i>
<i>Give me some clarity ♪</i>

13:25.805 --> 13:30.808
<i>♪ Time for your</i>
<i>couture love to rule! ♪</i>

13:30.810 --> 13:33.311
<i>♪ The Rules of Rarity!</i>
<i>Extra TLC ♪</i>

13:33.313 --> 13:35.646
<i>♪ This feels more sublime! </i>

13:35.648 --> 13:38.349
<i>♪ Soon now they will see</i>
<i>how good these can be ♪</i>

13:38.351 --> 13:40.551
<i>♪ with a little extra shine! </i>

13:40.553 --> 13:42.887
<i>♪ The Rules of Rarity!</i>
<i>Guaranteed Quality! ♪</i>

13:42.889 --> 13:45.323
<i>♪ All can see it's true! </i>

13:45.325 --> 13:50.027
♪ These new gems add such flare
<i>Their beauty can't compare ♪</i>

13:50.029 --> 13:53.364
<i>♪ This old style</i>
<i>suddenly gleams anew! ♪</i>

13:53.366 --> 13:57.601
♪

13:59.638 --> 14:00.905
[bell jangles]

14:03.975 --> 14:06.877
Is that the customer who
ordered this Princess Dress?

14:08.814 --> 14:11.382
I'll take care of
her. You keep working.

14:11.384 --> 14:13.818
Uhh, actually, I'd love
to see her reaction

14:13.820 --> 14:15.820
to this particular dress.

14:15.822 --> 14:17.788
Paisley and Poplin, Rarity!

14:17.790 --> 14:19.957
Look at all the orders
you still have to finish!

14:19.959 --> 14:22.760
And you want to
take a break? Now?

14:22.762 --> 14:26.130
Well, it's just...I made
some really lovely changes

14:26.132 --> 14:27.398
to this dress.

14:27.400 --> 14:32.970
But every Princess Dress is
supposed to be exactly the same!

14:32.972 --> 14:36.073
Yes, yes, I know. But these
gems just spoke to me.

14:36.075 --> 14:38.809
Fine. Go see her reaction.

14:40.879 --> 14:43.981
Hello, and welcome to
Canterlot Carousel.

14:43.983 --> 14:47.118
I am so pleased to
present to you your...

14:47.120 --> 14:49.954
PRINCESS DRESS! Finally!

14:49.956 --> 14:51.889
I've been simply
desperate to get this

14:51.891 --> 14:54.625
ever since I saw Princess
Twilight wearing it at your...

14:54.627 --> 14:59.497
Wait a minute. There's
something different.

14:59.499 --> 15:02.533
Well, as an artiste,
I did take the liberty

15:02.535 --> 15:04.702
to change a few minor details.

15:06.705 --> 15:09.874
I...I saw these gems
glistening in the light

15:09.876 --> 15:11.642
and they just spoke to me.

15:11.644 --> 15:14.779
Aren't they lovely?
And so unique?

15:14.781 --> 15:20.151
They're fine. But they're not
what I ordered, are they?

15:20.153 --> 15:23.087
No...no, they're not.

15:23.089 --> 15:25.723
I want the dress to be
exactly like the one

15:25.725 --> 15:28.559
Princess Twilight
wore. Understand?

15:28.561 --> 15:30.928
Yes. Yes, of course.

15:30.930 --> 15:38.002
♪

15:39.104 --> 15:44.575
<i>♪ The Rules of Rarity</i>
<i>Once stood for something ♪</i>

15:44.577 --> 15:49.780
<i>♪ But now it feels just</i>
<i>like some factory ♪</i>

15:49.782 --> 15:55.085
<i>♪ Now every dress I make</i>
<i>With every flaw and mistake ♪</i>

15:55.087 --> 16:02.159
<i>♪ Oh, how it makes my heart,</i>
<i>my heart, just break! ♪</i>

16:09.100 --> 16:16.173
♪

16:20.479 --> 16:26.150
Raving ricrac, Rarity! You made
two hundred Princess Dresses!

16:26.152 --> 16:29.186
Yes. Isn't it spectacular?

16:29.188 --> 16:31.689
And I have a special
surprise for you!

16:31.691 --> 16:35.926
The latest issue of Cosmare
Magazine just hit the stands!

16:35.928 --> 16:38.662
Rarity: Canterlot's
Newest Rising Star!

16:38.664 --> 16:40.965
And in the hour since
the magazine's come out,

16:40.967 --> 16:44.702
we've gotten another hundred new
orders for the Princess Dress!

16:44.704 --> 16:46.570
[slam]

16:46.572 --> 16:51.275
One...hundred...more...
Princess Dresses?

16:51.277 --> 16:54.044
I'm the Cosmare Coverpony.

16:54.046 --> 16:56.981
I have the most successful
shop in Canterlot.

16:56.983 --> 17:02.219
I've gotten everything I ever
wanted, but...I'm...miserable.

17:02.221 --> 17:04.889
How could you
possibly be miserable?

17:04.891 --> 17:09.026
My pattern is perfect.
"COSMARE COVERPONY!" Done!

17:09.028 --> 17:13.163
You have your signature gown!
"THE PRINCESS DRESS: A SUCCESS!"

17:13.165 --> 17:16.000
I don't want to make another
hundred Princess Dresses!

17:16.002 --> 17:21.071
"ASSEMBLE THE ASSEMBLY LINE!"
You'll never have to sew again

17:21.073 --> 17:23.073
What? No!

17:23.075 --> 17:26.911
Yes! Then the "CANTERLOT
CAROUSEL NEVER CLOSES!"

17:26.913 --> 17:30.247
and "SASSY SADDLES'
BOUTIQUE SUCCEEDS!"

17:30.249 --> 17:33.817
Stop! This is not
your boutique!

17:33.819 --> 17:36.287
And if this is what success
in Canterlot looks like,

17:36.289 --> 17:38.622
I want no part of it.

17:38.624 --> 17:42.126
Now, make up flyers for a
Going Out of Business Sale!

17:42.128 --> 17:44.762
I'm closing
Canterlot Carousel!

17:44.764 --> 17:47.698
What? No! Oh, you
can't, Rarity!

17:47.700 --> 17:49.900
I've worked too hard
to make this a success!

17:49.902 --> 17:53.137
I can't be a part of...
ANOTHER FAILED BOUTIQUE!

17:53.139 --> 17:54.772
[slam]

17:54.774 --> 18:01.845
♪

18:06.151 --> 18:09.954
Oh, don't you look lovely! Nice
to see you out here again.

18:09.956 --> 18:14.091
♪

18:14.093 --> 18:15.693
Seems Sassy Saddles
isn't rushing

18:15.695 --> 18:17.328
to open the door
this time. Hmm.

18:19.664 --> 18:21.732
Welcome to the Going
Out of Business Sale

18:21.734 --> 18:23.200
of Canterlot Carousel.

18:23.202 --> 18:25.135
[clamouring]

18:25.137 --> 18:28.939
♪

18:28.941 --> 18:31.642
Hey, is this Princess
Dress on sale?

18:31.644 --> 18:34.678
No, I'm sorry, the Princess
Dress has been discontinued.

18:34.680 --> 18:37.982
But there are plenty of other
lovely dresses on sale today.

18:37.984 --> 18:42.319
Whoa. This dress completely
speaks to my soul.

18:42.321 --> 18:43.821
Can I try it on?

18:43.823 --> 18:47.024
Certainly! The dressing
area is right back there.

18:47.026 --> 18:50.160
This is the most amazing
of amazing dresses!

18:50.162 --> 18:53.063
Just looking at it
brightens my day!

18:53.065 --> 18:56.300
And I'm sure you'll feel even
brighter once you try it on!

18:56.302 --> 18:58.902
Do you still have this
In-Spire-ation dress

18:58.904 --> 19:00.671
that's in the new
issue of Cosmare?

19:00.673 --> 19:03.340
Oh, yes, I do! It's right here!

19:03.342 --> 19:06.877
Bats in the belfry!
I have to try it on!

19:06.879 --> 19:12.182
Whoa, this dress makes
me feel like a Princess.

19:12.184 --> 19:15.653
And this dress makes me
feel like a Princess!

19:17.989 --> 19:19.990
This gown is quite beautiful,

19:19.992 --> 19:23.060
but it totally clashes
with my complexion.

19:23.062 --> 19:27.898
Hmm. Perhaps you'd be even
more taken with this one.

19:27.900 --> 19:31.035
It was inspired by the fountain
in the Canterlot Castle Garden.

19:31.037 --> 19:33.771
I call it, "The
Fountain of Truth."

19:33.773 --> 19:36.106
It's exactly what
I've been dreaming of!

19:36.108 --> 19:39.677
Ooh! Well, then, I'll finish it
and the gown shall be yours!

19:41.179 --> 19:43.113
How could I have forgotten?

19:43.115 --> 19:46.016
This is what I've
been dreaming about!

19:46.018 --> 19:47.851
♪

19:47.853 --> 19:52.089
<i>♪ My favorite moment's</i>
<i>when a pony sees it ♪</i>

19:52.091 --> 19:56.860
<i>♪ That special gown</i>
<i>that she just adores ♪</i>

19:56.862 --> 20:01.465
<i>♪ That pony's now in style</i>
<i>My hard work's all worthwhile ♪</i>

20:01.467 --> 20:08.005
<i>♪ Oh, yes, it makes my</i>
<i>heart, my heart, just soar! ♪</i>

20:08.007 --> 20:11.108
♪

20:11.110 --> 20:16.380
Attention everypony! Canterlot
Carousel WILL NOT be closing!

20:16.382 --> 20:18.849
[cheers]

20:18.851 --> 20:22.720
But this stuff's
still on sale, right?

20:22.722 --> 20:25.189
Yes, yes, of course.

20:25.191 --> 20:28.025
Oh, Rarity,
I'm so sorry!

20:28.027 --> 20:30.227
I focused on that
one dress

20:30.229 --> 20:33.864
and the rest of Rarity's
Royal Regalia paid the price.

20:33.866 --> 20:36.166
Well, so did the
Princess Dress.

20:36.168 --> 20:38.368
The more I sewed, the
more each dress lost its

20:38.370 --> 20:44.374
Time, Love, and Couture becoming
Terrible, Lackluster and Common.

20:44.376 --> 20:48.078
I think I finally understand
the Rules of Rarity

20:48.080 --> 20:51.181
and will apply them
at my next job.

20:51.183 --> 20:52.416
I beg your pardon?

20:52.418 --> 20:54.251
The Rules of Rarity
are only to be applied

20:54.253 --> 20:56.019
at Canterlot Carousel.

20:56.021 --> 20:59.022
Which is why you must continue
to manage the boutique

20:59.024 --> 21:00.457
while I'm in Ponyville.

21:00.459 --> 21:04.161
Well, yes, I'll come to
Canterlot with new designs

21:04.163 --> 21:05.929
and to see the
customers, of course,

21:05.931 --> 21:09.066
but Ponyville was always
going to be my home base.

21:09.068 --> 21:11.168
Bobbins and
bodkins, Rarity!

21:11.170 --> 21:12.936
Oh, thank you,
thank you!

21:12.938 --> 21:17.074
And I promise to run everything
following your rules!

21:17.076 --> 21:19.076
I would expect
nothing less!

21:20.245 --> 21:24.414
OH MY GOSH! A SALE?! DO YOU
HAVE THAT PRINCESS DRESS?

21:24.416 --> 21:25.415
NO!

21:25.417 --> 21:27.951
[laughter]

21:32.290 --> 21:34.958
♪ <i>My Little Pony</i> ♪

21:36.461 --> 21:39.129
♪ <i>My Little Pony</i> ♪

21:49.507 --> 21:51.809
♪ <i>My Little Pony</i> ♪

21:51.811 --> 21:55.879
<i>♪ friends </i>
